{"tid":1593825,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"守護孩子成員Yellow Man正休養 壓力大暫未決定投訴與否","createTime":"2019-09-25T08:56:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T08:58:07.000Z","uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ad22ce0530d6ccda7214b2bc363e6fc5ce0e211b","tid":1593825,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T08:56:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190925/large/1569383825_56e5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190925%2Flarge%2F1569383825_56e5.jpg&h=c2c85080&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方9.21在元朗鳳攸北街一帶截查及拘捕多人期間，故意將包括一名身穿橙黃色背心的「守護孩子行動」男成員拖入後巷，制服該名黃衣人後仍用腳踢向他，其間阻止記者拍攝。警方其後否認對黃衣人濫用私刑，又貶稱該男子為「Yellow Object」，可以是一個人、一個袋或一件背心。有份組織「守護孩子」的好鄰舍北區教會傳道人陳凱興今早在港台節目直斥警方說法非常可恥及可惡，將人當成物件是邪惡，令人氣憤，指已聯絡拍攝到片段的街坊，對方肯定被警方腳踢的是人，他們會收集不同片段再跟進。他又說，被踢的成員現時在家休養，身體狀況良好，但需要時間緩衝，待休養好後再視乎跟進行動。他稱當時人現時壓力大，未思考會否就事件投訴。<br />\n<br />\n陳凱興說，今次是首次有成員被捕，將影響將來與警方互動，「守護孩子行動」的工作會繼續，但會為成員提供更多訓練和支援。<br />\n<br />\n陳伯等多名行動成員9.21亦遭警員迎面噴射胡椒噴劑，陳伯今日接受港台訪問時，憶述當日見到一名青年被警員拉入後巷後，便與警方理論，要求得知青年名字以便找社工跟進，強調當時並無任何衝突，但突然有一隊穿着警員背心的人衝來，同時站在盾牌後，正與他理論的警員在全無警告下拿出胡椒噴劑向他噴射，其他警員亦衝前大力猛撞他，令他跌倒在場，未能睜開眼睛。陳伯即時質問警員為何推撞他，他所犯何事？但當時有其他警員推開他，放走該名推撞的警員。陳伯睜開眼睛後，看到身邊有另一名身穿黃衣的人士，相信是隊友，當時兩名警員按着黃衣人的頭將他拖入後巷，陳伯未能阻止。陳伯怒斥警方「一錯再錯」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190925/60082052?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190925%2F60082052%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=ZBayvnjX3omFcj6xyood9CQscPELFEQk1IFn5y5IyWs%3D&h=896ae7c0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190925%2F60082052%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=06a75984\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190925/60082052?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"7c80740396f02ad0268da575a4d92086dfe0e532","tid":1593825,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T08:58:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">國&hearts;際&hearts;戰&hearts;線&hearts;需&hearts;要&hearts;你</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RH29z9Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRH29z9Z.jpg&h=787fa8fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">☆</span>Tg channel在此 <a href=\"http://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=ZBayvnjX3omFcj6xyood9CQscPELFEQk1IFn5y5IyWs%3D&h=4612c2f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/twittermansyunzou</a> <span style=\"color: gold;\">☆</span>"}]}